snippet: A jury found W. McKeeva Bush not guilty of charges that he illegally used his government credit card to withdraw nearly $50,000 at casinos in the Bahamas and the United States.
abstract: Cayman Islands jury finds former premier W McKeeva Bush not guilty of charges that he illegally used his government credit card to withdraw nearly $50,000 at casinos in the Bahamas and the United States.
lead_paragraph: A jury found W. McKeeva Bush not guilty of charges that he illegally used his government credit card to withdraw nearly $50,000 at casinos in the Bahamas and the United States.
